title: Bug #121170 - get_column_label from meta data object should return user recognizable strings
OB: The current implementation of the get_column_label function in the meta data object does not return user recognizable strings.
EB: The get_column_label function should return user recognizable labels that can be displayed to the end user.
SR: To fix this bug, update the get_column_label function to return the same labels before and after extraction.
